RequisitionedItemsReport is a BusinessTask
    owned by rq

    Patterns
        implements ManualTransaction
        implements StaticJava
            is report for Buyer, InventoryManager, PurchasingManager, ApplicationAdministrator
                category is "Transactions"
                report name is "RequisitionedItems"
				Description
                    Analyze the requisition orders for a company.
                    The report includes all requisition lines within a specified date range.
            Reports
                RequisitionedItemsReportReport

    Parameters
        RqhCompany              is an InventoryCompany
        CompanyGroup            is a GeneralLedgerCompanyGroup
        FrCreationDate          is Date
        ToCreationDate          is Date
        ReqLocation             is a RequestingLocation 


        Status                  is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Unreleased    value is "1"
                NeedsApproval value is "2"
                Rejected      value is "3"
                Processed     value is "4"
                Closed        value is "5"
                All           value is "6"
                InProcess     value is "7"
        RlnItemType             is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                All          value is "A"
                Inventory    value is "I"
                Nonstock     value is "N"
                Service      value is "S"
                SpecialOrder value is "X"
        CreatePoOnly            is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"
        ReportOption            is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Detail  value is "D"
                Summary value is "S"
        ReportSeq               is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                CompItemVendorReqLocation value is "1"
                    default label is "Company/Item/Vendor/Requesting Location"
                CompItemReqLocRequester   value is "2"
                    default label is "Company/Item/Requesting Location/Requester"
                CompReqLocRequesterItem   value is "3"
                    default label is "Company/Requesting Location/Requester/Item"
        PrintUnspscGtin         is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"


        PurchMajor              is AlphaUpper size 4 
        PurchMinor              is AlphaUpper size 4 
		VendorGroup
        Vendor                   
        	context of VendorGroup
        Item
        	context of VendorGroup                                         


        PurchFrLoc              is a VendorLocation 
        	context of VendorGroup


        CommodityCode
        	context of VendorGroup           
        InclExclPoCodes         is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Include value is "I"
                Exclude value is "E"


        InclExclMfrCd           is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Include value is "I"
                Exclude value is "E"



    Parameter Rules
        Status
        	initial value is "6"
            default to "6"
        RlnItemType
        	initial value is "A"
            default to "A"
        CreatePoOnly
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        ReportOption
        	initial value is "D"
            default to "D"
        ReportSeq
        	initial value is "1"
            default to "1"
        PrintUnspscGtin
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        InclExclPoCodes
        	initial value is "I"
            default to "I"
        InclExclMfrCd
        	initial value is "I"
            default to "I"
		VendorGroup
			if (Vendor entered or Item entered or PurchFrLoc entered or CommodityCode entered)
                default to RqhCompany.BusinessGroup
                if (RqhCompany entered)
                    constraint (RqhCompany.BusinessGroup = VendorGroup)
                        "InvalidVendorGroupForCompany"
				required
            constraint(Vendor entered or Item entered or PurchFrLoc entered or CommodityCode entered)	
                "VendorGroupCanBeEnteredOnlyWhenVendor/Item/PurchFrLoc/CommodityCodeEntered"
            

            

    Actions
        RequisitionedItemsReport is a Set Action
            allow unlimited concurrency
